From 600c834a988ddbcc30968ea19c953754bff7c35e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: =?UTF-8?q?Bartek=20Iwa=C5=84czuk?= <biwanczuk@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 6 May 2026 16:36:00 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 1/8] fix(ext/node): improve module hooks support

- Add empty shims for `node:sea` and `node:test/reporters` builtins
- Pass custom conditions from resolve hooks through to
  `op_require_resolve_exports` for CJS package exports resolution
- Translate `--import`/`--require` flags in the Node CLI arg shim
  so child processes spawned via `child_process` honor preload modules
- Fix `loadESMFromCJS` cycle error when load hooks return
  `format: 'module'` by using a data: URI for hook-provided source
- Make ESM load hook chain's `nextLoad` synchronous so sync hooks
  from `registerHooks()` get direct values instead of Promises
- Read file source from disk in ESM load hook chain's default load
  so hooks can inspect and transform module source
- Validate load hook `source` return property and throw
  `ERR_INVALID_RETURN_PROPERTY_VALUE` for invalid types
