Subject: [PATCH 2/8] test(compile): add spec test for module hooks in compiled
 binaries

Adds a regression test for #33853. The test verifies that
registerHooks() load hooks can intercept and transform external
(non-embedded) file loads in compiled binaries.

Currently fails: the load hook bridge in the EmbeddedModuleLoader
does not route external file loads through the JS hook chain.
